      "content": "i dont know what to do. everything just feels so empty now. he's been my whole world for ten years and now its just... gone. i wake up and for a split second i forget, then it hits me all over again and i just cant breathe. i dont see how i'm supposed to keep doing this every single day. i really dont.",
