      "content": "small steps. i don't even want to take a step. every time i try to move forward, it just feels like i'm dragging this massive, heavy thing behind me. i just want the weight to stop. i just want to be able to sleep and not have this constant, crushing pressure in my chest. it feels like there's no version of the future where this doesn't hurt. why should i have to keep fighting a battle i've already lost?",
